# 🏠 House Price Prediction Using Machine Learning

## 📌 Project Overview

This project was developed as part of the Future Interns Data Science & Analytics Internship.

The objective of this project is to build machine learning models capable of predicting house prices using housing-related features such as location, median income, population, total rooms, and housing age.

The project includes data preprocessing, exploratory data analysis, model building, evaluation, and visualization of insights.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Load and explore housing data
- Clean and preprocess the dataset
- Handle missing values
- Convert categorical variables into numerical form
- Train machine learning models
- Compare model performance
- Visualize important insights
- Generate business recommendations

---

## 📂 Dataset Information

Dataset: California Housing Dataset

Target Variable:
- median_house_value

Features:
- longitude
- latitude
- housing_median_age
- total_rooms
- total_bedrooms
- population
- households
- median_income
- ocean_proximity

---

